Notes: If discovered you may face capture, fines, or worse!
Displayed Text: V pripade odhaleni vam hrozi zatceni, pokuta nebo i neco horsiho!

Notes: You will be asked to leave, if you don't there will be consequences...
Displayed Text: Budete vyzvani, abyste odesli, a pokud tak neucinite, bude to mit nasledky...

Notes: If discovered you may face capture, fines, or worse!
Displayed Text: V pripade odhaleni vam hrozi zatceni, pokuta nebo i neco horsiho!

Notes: If caught you will pay this. Lose your witnesses. If underlined, it means you have been seen and need to escape the building.
Displayed Text: Pokud budete pristizeni, zaplatite tuto castku. Prijdete o svedky. Pokud je podtrzeno, znamena to, ze jste byli spatreni a musite z budovy utect.

Notes: Citizens may smell you before they see you! Take a shower.
Displayed Text: Obcane vas mohou citit drive, nez vas uvidi! Osprchujte se.

Notes: Expect shivers and a slow decline of health. Do something or go somewhere warmer.
Displayed Text: Ocekavejte tresavku a pomaly upadek zdravi. Udelejte neco nebo jdete nekam do tepla.

Notes: Movement speed penalty. If you sit or lie down, you'll fall asleep. Get some caffeine or some rest.
Displayed Text: Snizeni rychlosti pohybu. Pokud si sednete nebo lehnete, usnete. Dejte si trochu kofeinu nebo si odpocinte.

Notes: Be careful not to run on slippery surfaces! This will disappear on its own, or you can find a towel.
Displayed Text: Davejte pozor, abyste nebehali po kluzkem povrchu! Muzete si najit rucnik nebo pockat.

Notes: Movement speed penalty. Running will make it worse! This will disappear on its own, or you can find some painkillers.
Displayed Text: Snizeni rychlosti pohybu. Beh to jeste zhorsi! Bolest vas prejde anebo muzete najit nejake leky proti bolesti.

Notes: Health recovery is inactive. Get something to eat.
Displayed Text: Obnova zdravi je neaktivni. Dejte si neco k jidlu.

Notes: Health recovery is inactive. Get something to drink.
Displayed Text: Obnova zdravi je neaktivni. Dejte si neco k piti.

Notes: You're drunk! Movement speed & control penalty. This will disappear on its own.
Displayed Text: Jsi opily! Sankce za rychlost pohybu a ovladani. Ten zmizi sam od sebe.

Notes: Movement speed & control penalty. This will disappear on its own, or you can find somewhere to throw up.
Displayed Text: Trest za rychlost pohybu a ovladani. Ten zmizi sam od sebe, nebo si muzete najit misto, kde se vyzvracite.

Notes: Boost to maximum health and health regeneration.
Displayed Text: Zvyseni maximalniho zdravi a regenerace zdravi.

Notes: Boost to maximum health and health regeneration.
Displayed Text: Zvyseni maximalniho zdravi a regenerace zdravi.

Notes: Movement speed penalty. Find a splint to heal this.
Displayed Text: Snizeni rychlosti pohybu. Najdete si dlahu, ktera ji vyleci.

Notes: Vision penalty. This will disappear on its own, but painkillers can speed up recovery.
Displayed Text: Penalizace na videni. Ten zmizi sam, ale leky proti bolesti mohou urychlit zotaveni.

Notes: Incoming damage is increased. This will disappear on its own, but painkillers can speed up recovery.
Displayed Text: Prichozi poskozeni se zvysuje. To zmizi samo, ale leky proti bolesti mohou urychlit zotaveni.

Notes: Incoming and outgoing damage is decreased. This will disappear on its own.
Displayed Text: Snizuje se prichozi a odchozi poskozeni. To samo zmizi.

Notes: Slow decline of health. This will disappear on it's own but you could pass out first! Find a bandage.
Displayed Text: Pomaly upadek zdravi. Ten zmizi sam, ale nejdrive muzete omdlit! Najdete obvaz.

Notes: You are detained, security will target you if you attempt to escape. Remove by paying fees or successfully escaping
Displayed Text: Jste zadrzeni a pri pokusu o utek se na vas zameri ochranka. Odstraneni zaplacenim poplatku nebo uspesnym utekem

Notes: Boost to movement speed, maximum health and health regeneration.
Displayed Text: Zvyseni rychlosti pohybu, maximalniho zdravi a regenerace zdravi.

Notes: Alarm systems will target you, be sure to avoid them
Displayed Text: Poplasne systemy se na vas zameri, vyhnete se jim.

Notes: Unless anyone saw you hide, you're safe from pursuers.
Displayed Text: Pokud te nikdo nevidel se schovavat, jsi pred pronasledovateli v bezpeci.

Notes: Consume a Starch Kola product to satisfy this craving.
Displayed Text: Tuto touhu uspokojite konzumaci vyrobku Starch Kola.

Notes: You may experience a small amount of disorientation.
You will lose health rapidly! Find Charcoal Tablets to purge your system.
Displayed Text: Ztracis rychle zdravi! Rychle najdi zivocistne uhli, ktere ti pomuze.

Notes: This room contains toxic gas, leave immediately!
Displayed Text: Tato mistnost obsahuje toxicky plyn, okamzite ji opustte!
Zóny Echelon jsou uzavřené komunitní oblasti výhradně pro občany s vysokým sociálním statusem.
